metadata.name: Spring Breeze
metadata.description:
HANI HAYA, Commissioned by Ligaratus
worked in 2022

3149 × 4583 pixel, 300DPI
PNG

A bright, warm sunlight. Shining through the window, accompanied by the soft, gentle wind.
A faint scent of the earth, as we enjoy our cozy lunch time together. The spring breeze is arriving.


Derivative artwork of Forgotten Runes Wizards Cult:
Shaman Eizo of the Tower (#8696) & Shaman Beyna in the Shadows (#528)
